CssAbsoluteSize = enum
  xxSmall = "xx-small", xSmall = "x-small", small, medium, large,
  xLarge = "x-large", xxLarge = "xx-large", xxxLarge = "xxx-large"
CssAlphaValue = SomeNumber | CssPercentage
CssAngle = object
  value*: float
CssAnglePercentage = CssAngle | CssPercentage
CssAngleType = enum
  deg, grad, rad, turn
CssBaselinePosition = enum
  firstBaseline = "first baseline", lastBaseline = "last baseline"
CssBlendMode = enum
  normal, multiply, screen, overlay, darken, lighten,
  colorDodge = "color-dodge", colorBurn = "color-burn",
  hardLight = "hard-light", softLight = "soft-light", difference, exclusion,
  hue, saturation, color, luminosity
CssBoxEdge = enum
  contentBox = "content-box", paddingBox = "padding-box",
  borderBox = "border-box", marginBox = "margin-box", fillBox = "fill-box",
  strokeBox = "stroke-box", viewBox = "view-box"
CssCalcKeyword = enum
  e, pi, positiveInfinity = "infinity", negativeInfinity = "-infinity", NaN
CssColor = object
  repr*: string
CssColorSpace = CssPolarColorSpace | CssPolarColorSpace
CssColour = CssColor
CssColourSpace = CssPolarColourSpace | CssPolarColourSpace
CssContentDistribution = enum
  spaceBetween = "space-between", spaceAround = "space-around",
  spaceEvenly = "space-evenly", stretch
CssContentPosition = enum
  center, start, `end` = "end", flexStart = "flex-start", flexEnd = "flex-end"
CssCubicBezierEasingFunction = object
  repr*: string
CssDimension = CssLength | CssTime | CssFrequency | CssResolution
CssDisplayBox = enum
  contents, none
CssDisplayInside = enum
  flow, flowRoot = "flow-root", table, flex, grid, ruby
CssDisplayInternal = enum
  tableRowGroup = "table-row-group", tableHeaderGroup = "table-header-group",
  tableFooterGroup = "table-footer-group", tableRow = "table-row",
  tableCell = "table-cell", tableColumnGroup = "table-column-group",
  tableColumn = "table-column", tableCaption = "table-caption",
  rubyBase = "ruby-base", rubyText = "ruby-text",
  rubyBaseContainer = "ruby-base-container",
  rubyTextContainer = "ruby-text-container"
CssDisplayLegacy = enum
  inlineBlock = "inline-block", inlineTable = "inline-table",
  inlineFlex = "inline-flex", inlineGrid = "inline-grid"
CssDisplayOutside = enum
  `block` = "block", inline
CssEasingFunction = CssLinearEasingFunction | CssCubicBezierEasingFunction |
    CssStepEasingFunction
CssFilterFunction = object
  repr*: string
CssFlex = fr
CssFrequency = object
  value*: float

CssFrequencyType = enum
  Hz, kHz
CssGenericFontFamily = enum
  serif, sansSerif = "sans-serif", monospace, cursive, fantasy,
  systemUi = "system-ui", uiSerif = "ui-serif", uiSansSerif = "ui-sans-serif",
  uiMonospace = "ui-monospace", uiRounded = "ui-rounded", math, emoji, fangsong
CssGradient = CssPropertyValue
CssHue = CssAngle
CssHueInterpolationMethod = enum
  shorterHue = "shorter hue", longerHue = "longer hue",
  increasingHue = "increasing hue", decreasingHue = "decreasing hue"
CssImage = string | CssUrl | CssSrc | CssGradient
CssLength = object
  value*: float
CssLengthPercentage = CssLength | CssPercentage
CssLengthType = enum
  cap, ch, em, ex, ic, lh, rcap, rch, rem, rex, ric, rlh, vh, vw, vmax, vmin,
  vb, vi, cqw, cqh, cqi, cqb, cqmin, cqmax, px, cm, mm, Q, pc, pt
CssLinearEasingFunction = object
  repr*: string
CssLineStyle = enum
  none, hidden, dotted, dashed, solid, double, groove, ridge, inset, outset
CssOverflow = enum
  visible, hidden, clip, scroll, `auto`

  unsafe, safe
CssPercentage = percent
CssPolarColorSpace = enum
  hsl, hwb, lch, oklch
CssPolarColourSpace = CssPolarColorSpace
CssPosition = enum
  left, center, right, top, bottom
CssPropertyValue = string
CssRectangularColorSpace = enum
  srgb, srgbLinear = "srgb-linear", displayP3 = "display-p3",
  a98Rgb = "a98-rgb", prophotoRgb = "prophoto-rgb", rec2020, lab, oklab, xyz,
  xyzD50 = "xyz-d50", xyzD65 = "xyz-d65"
CssRectangularColourSpace = CssRectangularColorSpace
CssRelativeSize = enum
  smaller, larger
CssResolution = object
  value*: float
CssResolutionType = enum
  dpi, dpcm, dppx, x
CssSelfPosition = enum
  center, start, `end`, selfStart = "self-start", selfEnd = "self-end",
  flexStart = "flex-start", flexEnd = "flex-end"
CssSrc = object
  repr*: string
CssStepEasingFunction = object
  repr*: string
CssStepPosition = enum
  jumpStart = "jump-start", jumpEnd = "jump-end", jumpNone = "jump-none",
  jumpBoth = "jump-both", start, `end` = "end"
CssTextEdge = enum
  alphabetic, cap, ex, text
CssTime = object
  value*: float

  s, ms

  repr*: string

  repr*: string
